title: Kings of Leon (4 Albums @ 320 and 7 B-sides)
description:
This is by far my favorite band. I own all four of their albums, and I'm seeing them in concert in October.

I just want to share the great music.

All four albums ripped at 320 with Windows Media Player (sorry).
Youth & Young Manhood (2003)
Aha Shake Heartbreak (2005)
Because of the Times (2007)
Only by the Night (2008)

I also have some additional tracks that I found:
Only by the Night B-Sides
"Beneath the Surface" 
"Frontier City"

Because of the Times B-Sides
"My Third House" from On Call Single
"Woo Hoo" from Fans Single

"Wicker Chair" from Holly Roller Novocaine

"Where Nobody Knows" from The Bucket

"Head to Toe" from 4 Kicks Single

The extras are at various bitrates.

This is not a complete collection. I have no live recordings, and I am missing a couple remixes as well as the song "Molly's Hangover."
